  "title": "Tapping for massive cashflow",
  "subtitle": "A five-minute tapping script for releasing the ceiling on what income is allowed to be.",
  "excerpt": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 39 of the MONEY program. The script targets the habit of keeping income expectations small: the belief that six-figure months are for other people, that large cashflow is somehow unsafe or unrealistic.",
  "type": "PRACTICE",
  "sourceNotes": "Adapted from Day 39 of MONEY: A 12-Week Tapping Program (Rebecca J Page, 2025), \"Anchor belief in massive cashflow.\" Tapping framework: Gary Craig's Emotional Freedom Technique (EFT), in use since the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy.",
