        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 39 of the MONEY program. The script works on the specific belief that six- and seven-figure cashflow is reserved for other types of people or businesses. The karate chop names that belief directly.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to tapping? Read ",
